{"tid":499463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地單身女想為人母　赴澳洲揀澳男捐精誕女嬰","createTime":"2017-12-14T23:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T07:46:58.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"182482b4188ae7e0dfdb5693ea073c12caf56176","tid":499463,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T23:50:23.000Z","msg":"內地不少女性到了生育年齡卻苦無伴侶，想做媽媽，但因內地法律仍不容許未婚女性在捐精者協助下誕下試管嬰兒，所以有人就選擇跑到澳洲做人工受孕。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171213_CH_pregnant_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171213_CH_pregnant_1.jpg&h=2de265c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳凰在澳洲接受人工受孕，成功誕下女嬰（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n現年33歲的上海姑娘陳凰（Chen Huang，譯音），剛剛在澳洲分娩。非常喜歡小孩的她說，曾經試過找個男人來生小孩，但現在在情路上已放棄了希望。陳凰是看到一篇有關外國精子銀行的文章後，加入一個聊天群組，研究在海外接受人工授孕的可能性。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171213_CH_pregnant_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171213_CH_pregnant_2.jpg&h=a36d622a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳凰說她考慮了超過一年，才決定到澳洲接受人工受孕（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n陳凰表示，她考慮了超過一年，因為有很多問題都需要想清楚，例如孩子出生後怎麼跟親友交代、應不應該公開、孩子長大後，又應不應該告訴孩子真相等等。在思前想後她終於決定選擇到聲譽良好、生育技術先進的澳洲接受人工受孕。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171213_CH_pregnant_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171213_CH_pregnant_4.jpg&h=65026bad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n協助陳凰的靳醫生表示，近年來自中國的客人越來越多（設計圖片）<br />\n<br />\n陳凰光顧的是悉尼一間私人診所，幫她的是會說普通話及廣東話的靳醫生（Andrew Kan，譯音）。靳醫生表示，近年來自中國的客人越來越多，希望接受人工授孕的婦女，可以根據捐精者填寫的表格，了解他的種族、身體特徵、教育水平及病歷等，才選擇孩子生父。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171213_CH_pregnant_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171213_CH_pregnant_3.jpg&h=6fc762b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳凰表示，日後女兒如果問起自己如何來到這個世上，她會坦白告訴女兒真相（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n陳凰最後挑選了一位澳洲捐精者，在今年2月接受人工授孕，返回內地後發現自己成功懷孕，今年9月在父母陪同下，返回悉尼待產，並在上月剖腹誕下女嬰。陳凰認為，這是她最大的成就，也是生命中最快樂的時光，從此一切都改變了。她還表示，日後女兒如果問起自己如何來到這個世上，她會坦白告訴女兒真相。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2662830-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E5%A5%B3%E6%83%B3%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%AF%8D-%E8%B5%B4%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%8F%80%E6%BE%B3%E7%94%B7%E6%8D%90%E7%B2%BE%E8%AA%95%E5%A5%B3%E5%AC%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2662830-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2583%25B3%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AF%258D-%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%258F%2580%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%258D%2590%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E8%25AA%2595%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AC%25B0&d=QityVE64U90TG%2BhHdk7iNROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=df03912b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2662830-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E5%A5%B3%E6%83%B3%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%AF%8D-%E8%B5%B4%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%8F%80%E6%BE%B3%E7%94%B7%E6%8D%90%E7%B2%BE%E8%AA%95%E5%A5%B3%E5%AC%B0</a>"},{"pid":"1080ffb7e7526e1b8484503a658f00cff7c9f283","tid":499463,"uid":38946,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T23:52:44.000Z","msg":"返回悉尼待產，並在上月剖腹誕下女嬰。"},{"pid":"84ae3a884a29cc972fdbce42ed3e6da243fd0c86","tid":499463,"uid":6345,"like":181,"dislike":7,"score":174,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T23:57:03.000Z","msg":"精子：幾難得先做到澳洲撚 點撚解又要返返去終國<br />\n點解！"},{"pid":"f2a413439071e90d73c66cbd2ab4144d4a9d263d","tid":499463,"uid":1059,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T00:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為直接性交"},{"pid":"520cce933fdd8dadfef0cf19671524c